online banking our online banking service will help you track and control your finances all from the comfort of your home or office designed to save you time and money online banking allows you access to your bank accounts via the internet you can look up current balances transfer money between accounts and much more it is safe and secure and best of all it is free  online banking provides the following services selfenrollment realtime account balances and information realtime account detailsactivity with running balance transaction sorting and filtering assign transaction categories and memos create user reports based on transaction categories active statement for money web connect for quicken® stop payment onetime transfers repeating transfers user defined account alerts bill pay alerts secure mail online new account application deluxe® check orderreorder check imaging estatement presentment account preferences forgotten password system optional service bill payment safety and securitytelebank online banking and bill payment are not only accurate they are secure your personal information is protected by data encryption firewalls session timeouts and confidential personal passwords all of these measures are designed to prevent unauthorized access to dataour representatives will never ask you to reveal your password or pin and we will never send emails that prompt you to update or confirm sensitive personal information such as your social security number account number or mother’s maiden name we advise our customers never to respond to unsolicited requests for sensitive information regardless of whether such requests are made via telephone mail or email take a test drive click here to try a working demo of our online banking serviceenrollment is easyyou will need to provide and we will need to verify the following information before you may begin using online banking your checking or savings account number the date and ending balance from the last statement for your account your social security number your email address if you do not have a checking or savings account but would like to view your loan or cd account information online well collect your customer information today and our customer service department will activate your banking services within  business days click here to begin enrollment for online banking   quicken® is a registered trademark of intuit inc  deluxe enterprise operations inc all rights reserved   online banking community banking™personal online banking ibusiness banking™business online banking sign up for debit alerts quick links start the mortgage process your mortgage information credit card login consumer credit card information small business credit card information investments login asset management login myfamilycard cardholder login myfamilycard sponsor login by clicking the links below you will be leaving the bank website and will be redirected an outside website facebook posts by clicking the links below you will be leaving the bank website and will be redirected an outside website tweets tweets by bankatvillage newsletter signup helpful resources deposit rates loan rates online security privacy policy site map equal housing lender  member fdic home who we are what we offer solutions for you business commercial  institutional mortgage wealth  village bank  trust   w northwest highway arlington heights il     close close location staff and hours  village bank  trust follow us   online services atm  locations tools  calculators contact us home who we arephilosophy and mission contact us news and events meet the staff bank directors location staff and hours employment opportunities what we offeran overview deposit services loan services other services checking savings certificates of deposit credit cards maxsafe® accounts money smart online services platinum adventures® club solutions for youan overview individuals families kids and young adults starting out retirement years businesschecking  s