 cancel sector financials  industry banks  nec more from factset » description village bank and trust financial corp is a bank holding company the company has three active subsidiaries village bank the bank southern community financial capital trust i and village financial statutory trust ii the bank has one active subsidiary village bank mortgage corporation the mortgage company which is a full service mortgage banking company the company is the holding company of and successor to the bank the bank is the primary operating business of the company the bank offers a range of banking and related financial services including checking savings certificates of deposit and other depository services and commercial real estate and consumer loans primarily in the richmond virginia metropolitan area the bank offers a range of financial services and products and specializes in providing customized financial services to small and medium sized businesses professionals and individuals the bank conducts business from over  branch banking offices more from reuters » officers and directors craig d bell independent chairman of the board age  bio  compensation   reuters trading activity  yahoo finance william g foster jr chief executive officer of the company and the bank age  bio  compensation   reuters c harril whitehurst jr chief financial officer senior vice president age  bio  compensation   reuters jerry w mabry president and ceo of village bank mortgage corporation age  bio  compensation   reuters james e hendricks chief operating officer chief risk officer of company and the bank age  bio  compensation   reuters rebecca l kline executive vice president–retail of the bank age  bio  compensation   reuters max c morehead jr executive vice president commercial banking age  bio  compensation   reuters frank e jenkins jr director bio  compensation   reuters kenneth lehman director age  bio  compensation   reuters raymond thomas avery iii independent director age  bio  compensation   